Package: fmisc
Title: Miscellaneous R Package Development Utilities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides utility functions for R package development, including
    a comprehensive Makefile template with targets for building, checking,
    testing, documentation, and code quality tasks. Also includes a smart
    parallel computing framework that automatically selects the best
    parallelization backend based on operating system and available packages.
